      <title>州长顾问说，俄罗斯央行了解四月份的贷款趋势</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/russias-central-bank-understand-lending-trends-april-governors-advisor-says-2025-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯中央银行州长的顾问基里尔·特里索夫（Kirill Tremasov）周六表示，该银行将在4月会议上就关键利率进行充分了解贷款趋势，但现在谈论它还为时过早。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/russias-central-bank-understand-lending-trends-april-governors-advisor-says-2025-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 10:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
