      <title>硅谷银行的前父母可以提起193亿美元的FDIC诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/silicon-valley-banks-former-parent-can-pursue-193-billion-fdic-lawsuit-2025-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦法官裁定，硅谷银行的前父母可能会提起诉讼，以收回该银行2023年3月倒闭后扣押的19.3亿美元存款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/silicon-valley-banks-former-parent-can-pursue-193-billion-fdic-lawsuit-2025-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 15:56:09 GMT</pubDate>
