    <item>
      <title>劳埃德（Lloyds），全国范围</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/nationwide-first-direct-report-payments-problems-2025-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[劳埃德（Lloyds）和全国范围内的英国贷方在周五被IT故障打击了几个小时，这是由于立法者对银行的技术问题的审查增加了，这使客户无法获得服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/nationwide-first-direct-report-payments-problems-2025-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 09:37:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
