      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bbvas-battle-sabadell-heads-next-hurdle-with-competition-regulator-rule-2025-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙银行BBVA对小型竞争对手萨巴德尔（Sabadell）宣布的敌对竞标竞标10个月前宣布，在3月份竞争监管机构可能会宣布其审查结果时面临最新的测试。]]></description>
